cdata.name: LunarLink
cdata.desc:
LunarLink is a Blockchain-based staking platform. It grants users the access to its tools for investing in the cryptocurrency market, with the objective to provide a passive incomethrough a staking mechanism. In addition, LunarLink enables its users to invest in its mining facility as well as to utilize the platform mobile app, where it is possible to monitor the user investments.

The LNL token is an Ethereum-based (ERC-20) cryptocurrency. It is the token that powers the platform as it will be the medium to perform staking actions on the LunarLink.
